                  </persName>
             was indicted for <rs id="t18280911-54-off267" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18280911-54-off267" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280911-54-off267" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280911-54-cd268" type="crimeDate">4th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-54-off267 t18280911-54-cd268"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 4s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280911-54-victim427" type="victimName">
                        Alexander 
                        Brown
                     <interp inst="t18280911-54-victim427" type="surname" value="Brown"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18280911-54-victim427" type="given" value="Alexander"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18280911-54-victim427" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-54-off267 t18280911-54-victim427"></join>
                     </persName>
                  , from his person
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>ALEXANDER BROWN. I am a <rs id="t18280911-54-viclabel269" type="occupation">picture-frame maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-54-victim427 t18280911-54-viclabel269"></join>. On the 5th of September, I was passing through <placeName id="t18280911-54-crimeloc270">Bartholomew fair</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18280911-54-crimeloc270" type="placeName" value="Bartholomew fair"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18280911-54-crimeloc270" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-54-off267 t18280911-54-crimeloc270"></join>, at half-past nine o'clock in the evening, I felt a sudden pull at my pocket, turned round, and took hold of the prisoner's hand - he immediately dropped my handkerchief; I picked it up.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182809110047"></xptr>Prisoner. The property was found two yards before you, and I was behind you. Witness. I saw you drop it, and picked it up; there was nobody before us - he was close behind me; I put my hand round, and caught his hand before I even saw him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280911-54-person428">
                  JOHN 
                  BELTON
               <interp inst="t18280911-54-person428" type="surname" value="BELTON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280911-54-person428" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280911-54-person428" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I saw the prosecutor pick the handkerchief up, close to the prisoner's feet.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 16.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18280911-54-verdict271" type="verdictDescription">
